====================== to publish apps,polkagate.xyz =======

1- adjust @polkagate/extension-dapp version in packages/react-api/package.json

// to build the app, in the packages/apps/build
2- yarn build:www 

// DO NOT FORGET TO COPY "CNAME"
3- copy     packages/apps/build into ./docs 
push

add google tag:

<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-1N3FZCQQJM"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());

  gtag('config', 'G-1N3FZCQQJM');
</script>


in apps/public/index imediate after head tag

====================== to publish apps config=======

cd packages/apps-config/build

update package.json as follows  
    change "@polkadot/apps-config" to  "@polkagate/apps-config"
    adjust version

npm publish --auth-type=web --access public